snippet.title: Global Release Commemorative PV | Ninja Must die
snippet.description:
The Coolest Ninja Combat Game #NinjaMustDie is officially online!
Global Release Commemorative PV Unlocked!

Don’t miss out on our launch events, where you will be able to claim many rich rewards such as a free legendary weapon and many more!


🐱‍👤Official Website:
https://www.pandadagames.com

👇Download NOW!

https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pandadagames.ninja.global
